  "body": "# Bug Report\r\nFollow-up on design call from 19/06/23.\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nCurrently, if the user starts scrolling with opened keyboard, it remains open.\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe keyboard is collapsed when the user starts typing\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/4557972/bd63b403-9b27-4038-bbc9-7115ff8954d9\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n- keyboard is not closed; \r\n- causes an additional issue on IOS:\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/4557972/5726f434-79e3-47fe-8e4b-e5e5a338e167\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Open Status\r\n2) Set cursor to chat input\r\n3) Start scrolling\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 20/06/23\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
